OL,3,CTributes to 'kindhearted' teenager who
OL,4,Cdies in reservoir
OL,6,FTributes have been paid to a teenager
OL,7,Fwho died at a beauty spot after
OL,8,Fentering the water.
OL,10,FEmergency services were called to
OL,11,FDovestones Reservoir in Oldham on
OL,12,FFriday night (July 10) ater getting
OL,13,Finto difficulties at around 7pm.
OL,15,FThe victim has since been identified
OL,16,Fas 18 year old Karl Holland, with
OL,17,Femotional tributes being paid to the
OL,18,F"kindhearted, beautiful boy".
OL,20,FFriends have taken to Facebook and
OL,21,Fsocial media to pay tribute to Karl.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
