OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1783932715
OL,3,CTributes to 'kindhearted' teenager who
OL,4,Cdies in reservoir
OL,6,FMelissa Crockford wrote: "Rest in
OL,7,Fpeace Karl Holland absolutely heart
OL,8,Fbreaking."
OL,10,FJodie Newcomb added: "Forever in our
OL,11,Fhearts Karl so young but had one of
OL,12,Fthe biggest hearts there was."
OL,14,FA further tribute reads as:
OL,15,F"Absolutely tragic what a beautiful
OL,16,Fyoung kid rest your head Karl."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
