PN,36903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1783932715
OL,3,CTributes to 'kindhearted' teenager who
OL,4,Cdies in reservoir
OL,6,FWitnesses reported seeing a major
OL,7,Femergency services presence at the
OL,8,FSaddleworth beauty spot, with several
OL,9,Fpolice cars, fire engines, ambulances
OL,10,Fand an air ambulance called to the
OL,11,Fscene.
OL,13,FThe 18-year-old was found unresponsive
OL,14,Fand was pronounced dead at the scene.
OL,16,FDetective Inspector Steven Horton
OL,17,Fsaid: "We have tragically recovered
OL,18,Fthe body of an 18-year-old man from
OL,19,Fthe water and are conducting extensive
OL,20,Fenquiries to establish the full
OL,21,Fcircumstances.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,370,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1783932715
OL,3,CTributes to 'kindhearted' teenager who
OL,4,Cdies in reservoir
OL,6,F"Our thoughts remain with his family
OL,7,Fand friends during this incredibly
OL,8,Fdifficult time."JIt's understood his
OL,9,Fmother, Laura, died four years ago.
OL,11,FNaomi Rowbotham wrote: "Rest in peace
OL,12,FKarl you <was> a lovely boy who loved
OL,13,Fto have fun and laugh all the time
OL,14,Fwith my little brother I'm sure it was
OL,15,Fyour fault he grew <he's> hair like
OL,16,Fyou go find your mum up there she'll
OL,17,Fbe waiting for you sleep tight mate.
OL,19,FClaire Chesworth added: "RIP Karl, the
OL,20,Fonly comfort is you're back with your
OL,21,Fmum Laura! Both gone far too soon!"
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
