PN,36905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1783932715
OL,3,CTributes to 'kindhearted' teenager who
OL,4,Cdies in reservoir
OL,6,FLauren Garlick said: "Rip to this
OL,7,Fyoung man....such a tragic age to
OL,8,Fpass. I hope you and your mum are
OL,9,Freunited."
OL,11,FAn amber heat-health alert is in place
OL,12,Ffor most of England until 9pm on
OL,13,FSunday, 12 July, with some areas
OL,14,Fexpected to get temperatures of up to
OL,15,F33 degrees.
OL,17,FDetective Inspector Steven Horton
OL,18,Fsaid: "I would like to take this
OL,19,Fopportunity to remind the public of
OL,20,Fthe dangers of open water.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,370,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1783932715
OL,3,CTributes to 'kindhearted' teenager who
OL,4,Cdies in reservoir
OL,6,F"We strongly encourage people to stay
OL,7,Fsafe and refrain from entering large
OL,8,Fbodies of water including reservoirs,
OL,9,Frivers, canals, or ponds.
OL,11,F"Your safety is our priority. Please
OL,12,Flook after yourselves and enjoy the
OL,13,Fweather safely."
OL,15,FGreater Manchester is continuing to
OL,16,Fconduct its enquiries.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
