OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,370,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1783932715
OL,3,CTributes to 'kindhearted' teenager who
OL,4,Cdies in reservoir
OL,6,FIt's the second tragedy in Greater
OL,7,FManchester in just 24 hours, following
OL,8,Fon from the death of a 49 year old man
OL,9,Fafter he got into difficulty at Sykes
OL,10,Freservoir at Alexandra Park in the
OL,11,FEdgeley area of Stockport on Thursday
OL,12,Fnight.
OL,14,FIt brings to 11 the number of people
OL,15,Fin the North West who have died in
OL,16,Fwater-related incidents this year.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/7
